{"tid":2281717,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"彭于晏遇路人指點臭臉　Show麒麟臂比中指","createTime":"2020-11-11T10:35:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-11T11:07:54.000Z","uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0ed6e39f863a8cdb4fbc60413756ecbd9598af7c","tid":2281717,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T10:35:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/6LjdcCIW0e_ZTmnyZXACtLrsAow=/2089x2835/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WBIRWAZ2BFD2LNQPR53W4DWONI.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F6LjdcCIW0e_ZTmnyZXACtLrsAow%3D%2F2089x2835%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWBIRWAZ2BFD2LNQPR53W4DWONI.JPG&h=679154fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【特勤中心、張哲鳴／台北報導】38歲彭于晏到對岸發展多年，今年因疫情影響多半時間待在台灣，他熱愛戶外運動，日前被讀者捕獲他到陽明山騎單車的身影。前天中午，《蘋果》記者又在彭于晏家附近的商店街上，看見他提著外送平台紙袋，一路往住家方向走去，期間不少路人認出他紛紛交頭接耳。突然不知何故，彭于晏猛一個轉身往後方比出「中指」手勢，表情相當嚴肅，隨後在附近走了1圈才返家。<br />\n<br />\n彭于晏主演的林超賢動作大片《緊急救援》原定是今年中國賀歲檔，無奈遇上武肺疫情，片商決定延檔1年，改在明年的春節檔再上映。9月時，他因主演導演許鞍華的新作《第一爐香》一同前往威尼斯影展非競賽單元出席世界首映，可惜評價不如預期，今年的作品似乎都不太順利。<br />\n<br />\n近來他似乎多待在台灣，不時會在IG曬出登山或騎車照，也貼過自家咖啡品牌的相關照片。上個月底，還見有親友貼出他去海邊玩空拍機身影，也見到他去看太麻里的老火車，日子過得自在休閒。<br />\n住家附近兜圈子<br />\n前天中午，《蘋果》在他住家附近商圈，見他紮起長髮束成小馬尾，戴藍帽，身穿休閒短褲和黑色背心，露出黝黑粗壯手臂，提著外送平台的紙袋，看似裝滿食物的盒子，走路步伐相當快速。<br />\n<br />\n一路上有不少粉絲認出他，驚呼見到野生的大明星，不過，彭于晏走到一半突然不知為什麼原因被驚動，以迅雷不及掩耳的速度猛回頭，在大街上比了「中指」手勢，即使戴著墨鏡，依然看得出他的表情嚴肅不悅，之後轉身到附近晃了1圈才返家。對於他究竟為何在大馬路上回頭比中指，記者聯絡他的經紀人，未有回應。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201104/32SCL25Y7ZHK5BNUXBJLEFNLMU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201104%2F32SCL25Y7ZHK5BNUXBJLEFNLMU%2F&d=yH4nd0T6GS6ufvAy6eHVEQFhK%2BZ0PNwQmNlOVL%2F21oE%3D&h=a7d030f9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201104%2F32SCL25Y7ZHK5BNUXBJLEFNLMU%2F&h=b41134af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201104/32SCL25Y7ZHK5BNUXBJLEFNLMU/</a>"},{"pid":"21af67c3a15fd79370b818fbee57c7ee832024a0","tid":2281717,"uid":43493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T10:36:57.000Z","msg":"垃圾護旗手"},{"pid":"4e1774b35ef1ab36237f32c11f26e6b9ce2c0f2d","tid":2281717,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T10:37:33.000Z","msg":"做左護旗手之後每況越下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://d87urpdhi5rdo.cloudfront.net/07-29-2020/t_d329e174db244818889f5368314872db_name_640_f16c110580f2f071585edcb380be3029.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd87urpdhi5rdo.cloudfront.net%2F07-29-2020%2Ft_d329e174db244818889f5368314872db_name_640_f16c110580f2f071585edcb380be3029.jpg&h=351c4fe1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/12316388435/641\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.gtimg.com%2Fnewsapp_bt%2F0%2F12316388435%2F641&h=0ccd5cc6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"621916c118943732bd60146ae7d93fd23b59fa54","tid":2281717,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T10:38:37.000Z","msg":"全盛時期<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200519/339450880266997760.jpeg/pjo_WsEuZ9uAdM9I23FtOKFkKRPIk38SnKDkYJyg5GA?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200519%2F339450880266997760.jpeg%2Fpjo_WsEuZ9uAdM9I23FtOKFkKRPIk38SnKDkYJyg5GA%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=22099eb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3876407/org/b3eb34c73f6cf5758f20254eb7b4332e.jpg/013ao37DwkndAf5lBkwefWhJUwpFQerpW_LWI1vy1iM?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F